-- Albanian Weightlifter Pulaku Gets Olympic Ban for Drug Test
-- B y   C h r i s t o p h e r   E l s e r
-- 2012-07-28T10:57:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-28/albanian-weightlifter-pulaku-gets-olympic-ban-for-drug-test.html
Albanian weightlifter Hysen Pulaku
was suspended from the London Olympics after testing for a
banned drug.  The 20-year-old was found to have used stanozolol in a test
administered July 23, according to a statement from the
 International Olympic Committee .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Christopher Elser at 
 celser@bloomberg.net  